 o WHERE o.quote.symbol = :quoteSymbol\"),\n    61→        @NamedQuery(name = \"orderejb.findByHoldingHoldingid\", query = \"SELECT o FROM orderejb o WHERE o.holding.holdingID = :holdingHoldingid\"),\n    62→        @NamedQuery(name = \"orderejb.closedOrders\", query = \"SELECT o FROM orderejb o WHERE o.orderStatus = 'closed' AND o.account.profile.userID  = :userID\"),\n    63→        @NamedQuery(name = \"orderejb.completeClosedOrders\", query = \"UPDATE orderejb o SET o.orderStatus = 'completed' WHERE o.orderStatus = 'closed' AND o.account.profile.userID  = :userID\") })\n    64→public class OrderDataBean implements Serializable {\n    65→\n    66→    private static final long serialVersionUID = 120650490200739057L;\n    67→\n    68→    @Id\n    69→    @TableGenerator(name = \"orderIdGen\", table = \"KEYGENEJB\", pkColumnName = \"KEYNAME\", valueColumnName = \"KEYVAL\", pkColumnValue = \"order\", allocationSize = 1000)\n    70→    @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.TABLE, generator = \"orderIdGen\")\n    71→    @Column(name = \"ORDERID\", nullable = false)\n    72→    private Integer orderID; /* orderID */\n    73→\n    74→    @Column(name = \"ORDERTYPE\")\n    75→    @NotBlank\n    76→    private String orderType; /* orderType (buy, sell, etc.) */\n    77→\n    78→    @Column(name = \"ORDERSTATUS\")\n    79→    @NotBlank\n    80→    private String orderStatus; /*\n    81→                                 * orderStatus (open, processing, completed,\n    82→                                 * closed, cancelled)\n    83→                                 */\n    84→\n    85→    @Column(name = \"OPENDATE\")\n    86→    @Temporal(TemporalType.TIMESTAMP)\n    87→    @PastOrPresent\n    88→    private Date openDate; /* openDate (when the order was entered) */\n    89→\n    90→    @Column(name = \"COMPLETIONDATE\")\n    91→    @PastOrPresent\n    92→    @Temporal(TemporalType.TIMESTAMP)\n    93→    private Date completionDate; /* completionDate */\n    94→\n    95→    @NotNull\n    96→    @Column(name = \"QUANTITY\", nullable = false)\n    97→    private double quantity; /* quantity */\n    98→\n    99→    @Column(name = \"PRICE\")\n   100→    @Positive\n   101→    private BigDecimal price; /* price */\n   102→\n   103→    @Column(name = \"ORDERFEE\")\n   104→    @Positive\n   105→    private BigDecimal orderFee; /* price */\n   106→\n   107→    @ManyToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)\n   108→    @JoinColumn(name = \"ACCOUNT_ACCOUNTID\")\n   109→    @JsonIgnoreProperties({\"orders\", \"holdings\", \"profile\"})\n   110→    private AccountDataBean account;\n   111→\n   112→    @ManyToOne(fetch = FetchType.EAGER)\n   113→    @JoinColumn(name = \"QUOTE_SYMBOL\")\n   114→    private QuoteDataBean quote;\n   115→\n   116→    @OneToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)\n   117→    @JoinColumn(name = \"HOLDING_HOLDINGID\")\n   118→    @JsonIgnoreProperties({\"account\", \"quote\"})\n   119→    private HoldingDataBean holding;\n   120→\n   121→    /* Fields for relationship fields are not kept in the Data Bean */\n   122→    @Transient\n   123→    private String symbol;\n   124→\n   125→    public OrderDataBean() {\n   126→    }\n   127→\n   128→    public OrderDataBean(Integer orderID, String orderType, String orderStatus, Date openDate, Date completionDate, double quantity, BigDecimal price,\n   129→            BigDecimal orderFee, String symbol) {\n   130→        setOrderID(orderID);\n   131→        setOrderType(orderType);\n   132→        setOrderStatus(orderStatus);\n   133→        setOpenDate(openDate);\n   134→        setCompletionDate(completionDate);\n   135→        setQuantity(quantity);\n   136→        setPrice(price);\n   137→        setOrderFee(orderFee);\n   138→        setSymbol(symbol);\n   139→    }\n   140→\n   141→    public OrderDataBean(String orderType, String orderStatus, Date openDate, Date completionDate, double quantity, BigDecimal price, BigDecimal orderFee,\n   142→            AccountDataBean account, QuoteDataBean quote, HoldingDataBean holding) {\n   143→        setOrderType(orderType);\n   144→        setOrderStatus(orderStatus);\n   145→        setOpenDate(openDate);\n   146→        setCompletionDate(completionDate);\n   147→        setQuantity(quantity);\n   148→        setPrice(price);\n   149→        setOrderFee(orderFee);\n   150→        setAccount(account);\n   151→        setQuote(quote);\n   152→        setHolding(holding);\n   153→    }\n   154→\n   155→    public static OrderDataBean getRandomInstance() {\n   156→        return new OrderDataBean(new Integer(TradeConfig.rndInt(100000)), TradeConfig.rndBoolean() ? \"buy\" : \"sell\", \"open\", new java.util.Date(\n   157→                TradeConfig.rndInt(Integer.MAX_VALUE)), new java.util.Date(TradeConfig.rndInt(Integer.MAX_VALUE)), TradeConfig.rndQuantity(),\n   158→                TradeConfig.rndBigDecimal(1000.0f), TradeConfig.rndBigDecimal(1000.0f), TradeConfig.rndSymbol());\n   159→    }\n   160→\n   161→    @Override\n   162→    public String toString() {\n   163→        return \"Order \" + getOrderID() + \"\\n\\t      orderType: \" + getOrderType() + \"\\n\\t    orderStatus: \" + getOrderStatus() + \"\\n\\t       openDate: \"\n   164→                + getOpenDate() + \"\\n\\t completionDate: \" + getCompletionDate() + \"\\n\\t       quantity: \" + getQuantity() + \"\\n\\t          price: \"\n   165→                + getPrice() + \"\\n\\t       orderFee: \" + getOrderFee() + \"\\n\\t         symbol: \" + getSymbol();\n   166→    }\n   167→\n   168→    public String toHTML() {\n   169→        return \"<BR>Order <B>\" + getOrderID() + \"</B>\" + \"<LI>      orderType: \" + getOrderType() + \"</LI>\" + \"<LI>    orderStatus: \" + getOrderStatus()\n   170→                + \"</LI>\" + \"<LI>       openDate: \" + getOpenDate() + \"</LI>\" + \"<LI> completionDate: \" + getCompletionDate() + \"</LI>\"\n   171→                + \"<LI>       quantity: \" + getQuantity() + \"</LI>\" + \"<LI>          price: \" + getPrice() + \"