"</LI>\");\n   113→        }\n   114→        return ret;\n   115→    }\n   116→\n   117→    public void print() {\n   118→        Log.log(this.toString());\n   119→    }\n   120→\n   121→    public BigDecimal getGainPercent() {\n   122→        if (gainPercent == null) {\n   123→            gainPercent = FinancialUtils.computeGainPercent(getTSIA(), getOpenTSIA());\n   124→        }\n   125→        return gainPercent;\n   126→    }\n   127→\n   128→    public BigDecimal getTSIA() {\n   129→        return TSIA;\n   130→    }\n   131→\n   132→    public void setTSIA(BigDecimal tSIA) {\n   133→        TSIA = tSIA;\n   134→    }\n   135→\n   136→    public BigDecimal getOpenTSIA() {\n   137→        return openTSIA;\n   138→    }\n   139→\n   140→    public void setOpenTSIA(BigDecimal openTSIA) {\n   141→        this.openTSIA = openTSIA;\n   142→    }\n   143→\n   144→    public double getVolume() {\n   145→        return volume;\n   146→    }\n   147→\n   148→    public void setVolume(double volume) {\n   149→        this.volume = volume;\n   150→    }\n   151→\n   152→    public Collection<QuoteDataBean> getTopGainers() {\n   153→        return topGainers;\n   154→    }\n   155→\n   156→    public void setTopGainers(Collection<QuoteDataBean> topGainers) {\n   157→        this.topGainers = topGainers;\n   158→    }\n   159→\n   160→    public Collection<QuoteDataBean> getTopLosers() {\n   161→        return topLosers;\n   162→    }\n   163→\n   164→    public void setTopLosers(Collection<QuoteDataBean> topLosers) {\n   165→        this.topLosers = topLosers;\n   166→    }\n   167→\n   168→    public Date getSummaryDate() {\n   169→        return summaryDate;\n   170→    }\n   171→\n   172→    public void setSummaryDate(Date summaryDate) {\n   173→        this.summaryDate = summaryDate;\n   174→    }\n   175→}\n   176→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ac4f36ad-05ed-4d27-a34f-96d57675074f","uuid":"c81ec142-69e4-44ba-bd40-23ea044bc4c7"}
