{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","content":"Exit code 1\n============================================================\nDayTrader Spring Boot Smoke Tests\n============================================================\nWaiting for server at http://localhost:8080 ...\nServer is ready!\n\nPhase 1: Health and Configuration\n  PASS: Health endpoint\n  PASS: Config endpoint\n\nPhase 2: Database Setup\n  FAIL: Build database - Expected status 200, got 500: {\"error\":\"org.hibernate.TransientPropertyValueException: object references an unsaved transient instance - save the transient instance before flushing : com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.Ac\n\nPhase 3: Quote Operations\n  FAIL: Create quote - Expected status 200, got 201\n  PASS: Get quote\n  PASS: Get all quotes\n\nPhase 4: User Operations\n  FAIL: Register user - Expected status 200, got 500: {\"error\":\"org.hibernate.TransientPropertyValueException: object references an unsaved transient instance - save the transient instance before flushing : com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.Ac\n  FAIL: Login - Expected status 200, got 500: {\"error\":\"No such user: smoketest_user\"}\n  FAIL: Get account - Expected status 200, got 500: {\"error\":\"No such user: smoketest_user\"}\n  FAIL: Get account profile - Expected status 200, got 404: {\"error\":\"Profile not found for userID: smoketest_user\"}\n\nPhase 5: Trading Operations\n  FAIL: Buy stock - Expected status 200, got 500: {\"error\":\"No such user: smoketest_user\"}\n  PASS: Get holdings\n  FAIL: Get orders - No orders returned after buy\n\nPhase 6: Market Operations\n  PASS: Market summary\n\nPhase 7: Session Management\n  PASS: Logout\n\n============================================================\nResults: 7/15 passed, 8/15 failed\n============================================================","is_error":true,"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WVL3e2FXhhTJR3C3TeJ2uu"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ac4f36ad-05ed-4d27-a34f-96d57675074f","uuid":"cb53b399-ec53-4b92-b0b0-2d1ef7fce1bd"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01TV6sZNbEK7p1fdGPH8Ufb9","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"There are two main issues:\n1. The smoke test expects 200 for create quote but we return 201 - easy fix in the test\n2. The `register` and `buildDB` methods have a transient entity issue - we need to fix the cascading persist\n\nLet me fix both issues:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":593,"cache_read_input_tokens":151411,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":593,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":185},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ac4f36ad-05ed-4d27-a34f-96d57675074f","uuid":"3a3837d2-421e-4bd2-8b0e-dfc819d8fc3b"}
