{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","content":"Exit code 1\n============================================================\nDayTrader Spring Boot Smoke Tests\n============================================================\nWaiting for server at http://localhost:33660 ...\nServer is ready!\n\nPhase 1: Health and Configuration\n  PASS: Health endpoint\n  PASS: Config endpoint\n\nPhase 2: Database Setup\n  FAIL: Build database - Expected status 200, got 500: {\"error\":\"Error building database: A different object with the same identifier value was already associated with the session : [com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.AccountProfileDataBean#uid:\n\nPhase 3: Quote Operations\n  PASS: Create quote\n  PASS: Get quote\n  PASS: Get all quotes\n\nPhase 4: User Operations\n  FAIL: Register user - Expected status 201, got 500: {\"error\":\"A different object with the same identifier value was already associated with the session : [com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.entities.AccountProfileDataBean#smoketest_user]\"}\n  FAIL: Login - Expected status 200, got 500: {\"error\":\"No such user: smoketest_user\"}\n  FAIL: Get account - Expected status 200, got 500: {\"error\":\"No such user: smoketest_user\"}\n  FAIL: Get account profile - Expected status 200, got 404: {\"error\":\"Profile not found for userID: smoketest_user\"}\n\nPhase 5: Trading Operations\n  FAIL: Buy stock - Expected status 200, got 500: {\"error\":\"No such user: smoketest_user\"}\n  PASS: Get holdings\n  FAIL: Get orders - No orders returned after buy\n\nPhase 6: Market Operations\n  PASS: Market summary\n\nPhase 7: Session Management\n  PASS: Logout\n\n============================================================\nResults: 8/15 passed, 7/15 failed\n============================================================","is_error":true,"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01DUzc5oJ4pdHzyYhPJpjhSP"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ac4f36ad-05ed-4d27-a34f-96d57675074f","uuid":"4b2049f1-c60a-46f6-a769-71c4b7a16928"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_012N1aTdVgN8kJ5hvWh985Ju","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Progress! We went from 7 to 8 passing (create quote now passes), but the register issue persists. The error is: \"A different object with the same identifier value was already associated with the session\". This happens because we save the profile first (making it a managed entity), then set `account.setProfile(profile)` and save account with `CascadeType.ALL`, which tries to cascade-persist the already-managed profile object.\n\nThe fix is to not cascade on the account-to-profile relationship. Instead, save profile independently first, then save account with the profile reference. Or alternatively, remove the cascade and handle the save order explicitly.\n\nLet me rethink the approach. The issue is:\n1. `accountProfileRepository.save(profile)` - profile is now managed by the session\n2. `account.setProfile(profile)` - account references the managed profile\n3. `accountRepository.save(account)` with `cascade = ALL` tries to cascade-persist profile again, but it's already in session with same ID\n\nThe simplest fix is to remove the cascade and explicitly manage the save order:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":571,"cache_read_input_tokens":74522,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":571,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":510},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ac4f36ad-05ed-4d27-a34f-96d57675074f","uuid":"ca094c0b-5a27-49ad-a8f4-6d6b9eedea0a"}
