{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01DQz9wRJ5w8VsGGJ9JarGif","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Migration Complete - Summary\n\nThe DayTrader application has been successfully migrated from Jakarta EE (Open Liberty) to Spring Boot 3.2.5. Here's the final status:\n\n### Results\n- **Docker build**: Succeeds (compiles cleanly with Java 17+)\n- **Application startup**: ~5 seconds\n- **Smoke tests**: **15/15 passed, 0/15 failed**\n\n### Key Changes Made\n1. **Build system**: Replaced Open Liberty/Java EE 8 Maven config with Spring Boot 3.2.5 parent\n2. **Entities**: Migrated `javax.persistence` -> `jakarta.persistence`; added JSON serialization annotations; implemented `Persistable<String>` on `AccountProfileDataBean` for proper Spring Data JPA handling of assigned IDs\n3. **Business logic**: Replaced EJB `TradeSLSBBean` with Spring `@Service` `TradeService`\n4. **Data access**: Created 5 Spring Data JPA repositories replacing direct EntityManager usage\n5. **REST API**: Created 6 Spring MVC `@RestController` classes replacing JAX-RS resources and Servlets\n6. **Removed**: EJBs, MDBs, JSF/XHTML UI, WebSocket, CDI beans, Servlets, Liberty configuration\n7. **Deprecated API fixes**: `new Float()` -> cast, `new Integer()` -> `Integer.valueOf()`, `BigDecimal.ROUND_HALF_UP` -> `RoundingMode.HALF_UP`\n\n### Key Technical Challenges Solved\n- **TransientPropertyValueException**: Resolved by implementing `Persistable<String>` on `AccountProfileDataBean` and ensuring correct entity save order (profile first, then account with FK reference)\n- **Circular JSON references**: Resolved with `@JsonIgnore` and `@JsonIgnoreProperties` annotations"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":121,"cache_read_input_tokens":106310,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":121,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":441},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ac4f36ad-05ed-4d27-a34f-96d57675074f","uuid":"24e51a77-3cf1-412f-b988-1bb6a9ded234"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":1844701,"duration_api_ms":2130929,"num_turns":166,"result":"## Migration Complete - Summary\n\nThe DayTrader application has been successfully migrated from Jakarta EE (Open Liberty) to Spring Boot 3.2.5. Here's the final status:\n\n### Results\n- **Docker build**: Succeeds (compiles cleanly with Java 17+)\n- **Application startup**: ~5 seconds\n- **Smoke tests**: **15/15 passed, 0/15 failed**\n\n### Key Changes Made\n1. **Build system**: Replaced Open Liberty/Java EE 8 Maven config with Spring Boot 3.2.5 parent\n2. **Entities**: Migrated `javax.persistence` -> `jakarta.persistence`; added JSON serialization annotations; implemented `Persistable<String>` on `AccountProfileDataBean` for proper Spring Data JPA handling of assigned IDs\n3. **Business logic**: Replaced EJB `TradeSLSBBean` with Spring `@Service` `TradeService`\n4. **Data access**: Created 5 Spring Data JPA repositories replacing direct EntityManager usage\n5. **REST API**: Created 6 Spring MVC `@RestController` classes replacing JAX-RS resources and Servlets\n6. **Removed**: EJBs, MDBs, JSF/XHTML UI, WebSocket, CDI beans, Servlets, Liberty configuration\n7. **Deprecated API fixes**: `new Float()` -> cast, `new Integer()` -> `Integer.valueOf()`, `BigDecimal.ROUND_HALF_UP` -> `RoundingMode.HALF_UP`\n\n### Key Technical Challenges Solved\n- **TransientPropertyValueException**: Resolved by implementing `Persistable<String>` on `AccountProfileDataBean` and ensuring correct entity save order (profile first, then account with FK reference)\n- **Circular JSON references**: Resolved with `@JsonIgnore` and `@JsonIgnoreProperties` annotations","session_id":"ac4f36ad-05ed-4d27-a34f-96d57675074f","total_cost_usd":38.935805840000015,"usage":{"input_tokens":8615,"cache_creation_input_tokens":473116,"cache_read_input_tokens":12859413,"output_tokens":66384,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache